人等等。<br />\n<br />\n3. 返工。我帶細路去戶外的。日日用，最緊要係慢慢學識左同小朋友互串。<br />\n<br />\n到有一日露營時發夢，夢入面用英文同人嗌交，醒左之後就覺得我d英文真係得得地喎。。。咁lor."},{"pid":"0e5402a55b67c9aa8bfff8d6cb2acf7f0edcf764","tid":920912,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cabda0bd0a7827bef41722119b0562f1cd8bdd21","tid":920912,"uid":199712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"睇pornhub學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"真係學左唔少生字。"},{"pid":"ec1f8619b6ad5436361996d9133a2800ef19e74c","tid":920912,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"YouTube， 有唔識嘅字就查字典"},{"pid":"11fe7d1f32684b8384ae60ff88f31bd04fbdd7c8","tid":920912,"uid":178989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"溝鬼妹"}]}